summary: This adds in 5 new staves with interesting effects.
descriptionHtml:
This adds in 5 new staves with interesting effects.

Bug Swarm Staff - Sprays the target in a swarm of bugs.

Staff of Blast Wave - A wave of fire blasts away your targets.

Dwarven Shocking Rod - Targets hit with this rod take shock damage and are paralzyed with electricty (DIsenchantable, then usable on any weapon)

Staff of Magicka Siphon - Siphons your targets magicka.

Staff of Paralyze Beam - Paralyzing your target for as long as you concentrate on it.

These Staves can all be found downstairs in Dragonsreach, on your way towards the whispering door you\'ll notice a barrel named the \"Staff Barrel\" contaniing all of the above mentioned staves (and one \"rod\"). The barrel is non respawning and player owned, so it\'s the perfect place to use as storage until you get your first house.
author: Stretch1one
